add_help_file

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_help_file -  This method sets up the help for the room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_help_file(string help_file)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^help_file%^RESET%^ - the help file name

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/help_files.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets up the help for the room.  All the help file names are
relative to /doc/room unless a complete path is specified.
.EP

